{"tid":1684730,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人唔係要完成一場「革命」 而係要成就一場 革命","createTime":"2019-10-31T08:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T10:40:26.000Z","uid":44367,"like":77,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"47889c7a88918d13718498452828b082e83cfd49","tid":1684730,"uid":44367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"有人話<br />\n<br />\n全民勇武做唔到<br />\n全民罷工做唔到<br />\n<br />\n所以要承認自己並唔係搞緊革命<br />\n<br />\n我想以正視聽 <br />\n<br />\n就算你全民勇武<br />\n全民罷工<br />\n<br />\n只要中共唔跪低 林鄭政府唔倒台<br />\n你唔成功 呢場運動就叫做暴動<br />\n<br />\n反而不論你用任何方法 <br />\nPart time抗爭<br />\n鳩叫口號 <br />\n整連儂牆/連儂畫<br />\n叫國際支援<br />\n文宣 <br />\n靜坐<br />\n罷買買搭<br />\n建立黃色經濟圈<br />\n唱歌<br />\n剪片放上網<br />\n香港獨立<br />\n做乜好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只有成功達成五大訴求 落實真普選<br />\n推倒港共政權 <br />\n<br />\n呢一場運動先可以由我地係歷史中正式命名為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「<br />\n革<br />\n命<br />\n」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地全部香港人都係極權下既受害者<br />\n不要再分化 不要再指責了"},{"pid":"6fe91d9488cac283b7c400ffb140d1b3699e4b98","tid":1684730,"uid":44367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:50:07.000Z","msg":"不成功 便成仁<br />\n成功 你就係時代英雄<br />\n失敗 就係狗雄"},{"pid":"debf4d1cf22d873d08f9078e0f72c6b33cedd2c4","tid":1684730,"uid":221988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:50:15.000Z","msg":"[推上熱門] 唔想再失去任何一個手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1684370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1684370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4b334b5b6d6a818b1f377328646d2d7f1154889b","tid":1684730,"uid":98993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:51:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3083f2726bf13b51ae876105ca6243ad62a07b59","tid":1684730,"uid":44367,"like":2,"dislike":1,"sco