br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「<br />\n革<br />\n命<br />\n」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地全部香港人都係極權下既受害者<br />\n不要再分化 不要再指責了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:12:40.000Z","msg":"一日未完呢場運動 你憑咩話人鳩做？<br />\n鬼唔知二百萬人一人一腳都踩死班狗<br />\n<br />\n大家都用緊各自既方法去做<br />\n你唔能夠好似陳雲咁 唔跟佢方法就話人賣港 話人累死人<br />\n<br />\n大家都要肯做個樣野 先有得講架"},{"pid":"ade74cb1d3605507a2eb85f5eb4fd39153725f20","tid":1684730,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"畀人恰到上心口"},{"pid":"46d7908794298b199554c068a37373815a229908","tid":1684730,"uid":36920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:17:00.000Z","msg":"講得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0491d84f4ca034b437ed44ce257c6fbd6a0e3d","tid":1684730,"uid":304845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:18:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"416915ea6d77d98fb97c33b532fc58cd3affc7a6","tid":1684730,"uid":304845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:19:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ee4cbe69270e068f7e06d9efed5c59c1c67a504","tid":1684730,"uid":195047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:24:07.000Z","msg":"做唔一定會贏 不過做就實有用<br />\n天琦講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有用就去做啦"},{"pid":"2649a40bad81588c6d0035ef6268d82183c767bc","tid":1684730,"uid":88334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:26:38.000Z","msg":"認同 堅持做自己相信嘅野<br />\n唔做咗先 永遠唔會知有咩結果<br />\n<br />\n好似天琦咁講 你信係work嘅就做<br />\n如果三罷得唔到認同 就做多啲文宣<br />\n<br />\n抗爭從來唔係一朝一夕嘅事<br />\n唔好忘記喺呢五個月<br />\n香港人已經創造咗無數奇蹟<br />\n唔好忘記如果唔係香港人企出黎<br />\n條惡法唔會撤回 而係已經過咗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好放棄呀香港人"},{"pid":"3ee66b9701f79eb5624532585d0537045e88a3c8","tid":1684730,"uid":320097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:32:36.000Z","msg":"唔只係香港 我地感染咗好多人 外國有熱潮 國內都有人啟蒙 我地夠長命就可以改變香港甚至中國"},{"pid":"85e7fbcfc71cd5b46174d139984848172657baa7","tid":1684730,"uid":44367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />堅持就有希望"}]}